{
  "stem": "1473.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these cousins, who are-- who lived in St.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Gallen, in German part of Switzerland, came-- came sort of to look me over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a mutual dislike, right there and then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, the OSE placed me with a family, with a Swiss family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were Swiss families who were willing to-- to take refugee children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I wound up in a place called [NON-ENGLISH] with a very, very loving Swiss family-- not at all my background.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were simple people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a foreman for the railroads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She-- they couldn't have children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they lavished a lot of affection on us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took the religion bit very, very seriously and made me go to a local rabbi, a Hebrew school, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The OSE supervised this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, the OSE thought that I needed to pick up my schooling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I went to-- passed an entrance examination, because I was a foreigner, to a specialized Swiss high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in 1945, I remember the landing, June 6.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was off from school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, of course, things began to look up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- oh, began to look up in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's-- in it, by itself, it held no-- you know, the Battle of [INAUDIBLE] held no interest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just, when am I going to hear from my mother and father?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's what all we talked about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we only talked about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, in April of 1945 these people, [FRENCH] Rose and [FRENCH] Louis had evidently received a letter for them to come with me to Geneva, to the head of the Swiss Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I lived with, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
